snippet.title: Across the Wonderlands - Official Re-announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Jump into a truly whimsical open-world survival crafting game!
Build your magical base dimension and craft fun dishes to battle quirky foes on your journey to the fallen star. 

Wishlist now!
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2597200/Across_the_Wonderlands/

Check out the Appetizer Demo!
https://store.steampowered.com/app/3260200/Across_the_Wonderlands__Appetizer_Demo/
